## 🎯 Daily Challenge

A system has:

* **Available = (3, 3, 2)**

| Process | Max     | Allocation |
| ------- | ------- | ---------- |
| P1      | (4,2,2) | (2,0,1)    |
| P2      | (2,2,2) | (1,1,0)    |
| P3      | (3,3,2) | (1,1,1)    |

1. Compute the **Need** matrix.
2. Determine whether the system is in a **safe state**.
3. If it is safe, write one valid **safe sequence**.

This style of numerical problem is one of the most common in GATE Operating Systems and is excellent practice for the exam.
